An empty jug pack is an item pack containing 100 noted jugs.

These packs can be bought at general stores for 140-182 coins each depending on the stock available, with the highest stocks being The Lighthouse Store and Ifaba's General Store, both of which stock eight packs.

They are not sold at the Bedabin Camp, Catherby, East Ardougne, West Ardougne, Shantay Pass, Tai Bwo Wannai, and Shilo Village general stores.
